author: Lego_fan_
title: A blue menace
review: This is a really cool keychain and I think it is one of the better ones from episode 1. It is a blue menace because I had to collect it and I always get distracted looking at it on my keyring or back pack. The only problem with this set is that watto's wings are made of rubber like in the set and they are at risk and have bent for me and I had to replace him. But other than that it is a really nice collectible for any Lego fan.
